  &lt;p class=&#34;wp-caption-text&#34;&gt;
    Church of St. John in the Wilderness. Nainital, India.
  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&#34;attachment_4341&#34; style=&#34;width: 710px&#34; class=&#34;wp-caption alignnone&#34;&gt;
