&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And thus, we spent several wonderful days exploring Nainital. Although we&amp;#8217;d been warned about noisy tourists and crowded attractions, we found the town to be quite peaceful and calm. Perhaps we were lucky to have escaped the peak tourist season.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
